ated precision, reflecting the enduring essence of high-quality heritage apparel. The Movement collection seamlessly blends the spirit of activity with the power of the present moment. These pieces are designed not just for performance but also as a statement of vitality.<\/p>","button_label":"","button_link":"","buttons_style":"filled","section_padding_top":0,"section_padding_bottom":0,"text_overlapping_image":false,"section-width":"full","layout":"right","text_alignment":"center","colors":"light"}},"testimonials_ikqQfc":{"type":"testimonials","blocks":{"text_TiB8TU":{"type":"text","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/754A0446-min.webp","testimonial_text":"<p>My husband says the Galt Sand sweatpants are the best quality he’s ever owned. The material is thick and durable, and they keep their shape longer than other brands.<\/p>","customer_name":"Vilhelmiina Huuskonen","link":"shopify:\/\/products\/heritage-jogger","stars":5}},"text_KHRU8K":{"type":"text","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Piquetee3.jpg","testimonial_text":"<p>I love these shirts.<\/p>","customer_name":"Jens Utermark","link":"shopify:\/\/products\/pique-short-sleeve","stars":5}},"text_nexrCF":{"type":"text","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/754A6595_5.jpg","testimonial_text":"<p>Good quality joggers, true to size and well made.<\/p>","customer_name":"Hamdy Ammar","link":"shopify:\/\/products\/pintuck-jogger","stars":5}},"text_RGWeAJ":{"type":"text","disabled":true,"settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/1123_8b4167fa-9c86-4b58-b11c-4ac0368095cf.webp","testimonial_text":"<p>Good quality clothes<\/p>","customer_name":"Tafa Dzinoruma","link":"shopify:\/\/products\/pique-quarter-zip","stars":5}}},"block_order":["text_TiB8TU","text_KHRU8K","text_nexrCF","text_RGWeAJ"],"custom_css":[".testimonial-section--image img {max-width: 424px; min-height: 492px;}"],"settings":{"circle_images":false,"title":"Testimonials","description":"","section_padding_top":60,"section_padding